Judith Arlen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judith_Arlen 0 Judith Arlen (born Laurette Elizabeth Rutherford; March 18, 1914 – June 5, 1968) was a Canadian-American film actress. She was the elder sister of actress Ann Rutherford. Judith_Arlen ( born Laurette_Elizabeth_Rutherford ; March_18_,_1914 – June_5_,_1968 ) was a_Canadian-American_film_actress .
